the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S.</ENAMEX> point of view, are: <ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">1</ENAMEX>) This is an opportunity to consolidate the <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">Cold</ENAMEX>
