<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">resurgent Russia</ENAMEX>; and <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3</NUMEX>) This guarantees a continuing leadership role for the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">United States</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Europe</ENAMEX>, even as <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Europe</ENAMEX> creates and strengthens its own
