               Anti-expansion arguments break down into
<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> main categories. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">One</NUMEX> emphasizes that <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NATO</ENAMEX> is not a feel-good
